    <lb n="19"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">εἰ</unclear> σὺ μέν μοι καὶ τιμὴν περιτιθεῖς καὶ θέλεις με εἶναι ἀνθρωπ<gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="20"/>καὶ συνέστησας καὶ συνδούλοις καὶ συνεξελευθέροις, ὅπερ ἐμ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">οὶ</unclear> 

    <lb n="21"/>χρήματά ἐστιν παρὰ σοὶ κ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αὶ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">οὗ</unclear> <choice><corr>ὑβρίζω</corr><sic><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">υβ</unclear>ριζωι</sic></choice> το<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῖ</supplied>ς γεγονόσι πλουσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ίοι</unclear>ς παρὰ τὸν 

    <lb n="22"/>σύνδουλόν σου καὶ συνεξελεύθερον. <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">παρ᾽ ἕκαστα δὲ ὁ Ἔρως <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὁ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σὸς</unclear> <gap extent="4" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del> 

